text: "Revhead" may refer to: * car enthusiast (term used in Australia) * A fan of the rock group, The Revivalists (New Orleans) * "hoon" or "boy racer" (term used in Australia) * Revhead (Home and Away), fictional character in Australian soap opera Home and Away * You're a Revhead, a 2011 compilation by Australian musician Adam Brand.
title: Revhead
